{"tid":224423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]這樣太性感！女星穿著太暴露　遭柬埔寨政府封殺一年","createTime":"2017-05-01T05:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T07:40:40.000Z","uid":42536,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"924086eeb21b294bcf25d4cb590dfc93659c526e","tid":224423,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"女權當道，女性對於身體自主權的意識也逐漸抬頭，不過柬埔寨的性感女星Denny Kwan卻遭政府當局以「過分性感」為由，禁止其任何的娛樂演出工作，讓當地網友都相當不解。<br />\n據《環球網》報導，Denny Kwan是柬埔寨著名的性感女星，她經常在臉書或是YouTube上傳不少清涼照或影片大秀好身材，不過此舉似乎是惹惱了柬埔寨當局，在近日柬國文化部就以「過分性感」為由，禁止她接演任何娛樂演出一整年，等同就是要「封殺」Denny Kwan一整年。<br />\n消息一出後，讓柬國網友都相當納悶，認為整個柬埔寨到全世界穿著性感的女星那麼多，為何就只封殺Denny Kwan；至於苦主Denny Kwan則表示「怎麼打扮是我的權利，但要是我們的國民和政府不接受，那日後我就會盡量不再上傳照片。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/28/891340-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F891340-XXL.jpg&h=5308e17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/28/891341-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F891341-XXL.jpg&h=c8adad12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/28/891342-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F891342-XXL.jpg&h=bf337fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/28/891343-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F891343-XXL.jpg&h=2496338d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=247739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D247739&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f57c3127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D247739&h=e5607ca7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=247739</a>"},{"pid":"83d79641fb0dd9843a1c4bb4757fa7575f44df9b","tid":224423,"uid":29445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"對波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96624167e99c4612fcf42e45541edb3691ce4098","tid":224423,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"對波咁假唔著衫都冇性慾啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6de3e767fc2c8375c128a1e6b8903c94f6c8ea1","tid":224423,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"d 奶假既"},{"pid":"6702ca4a4e056b0e9510ec51c052d4c922b0c68f","tid":224423,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d25b4971cd2496337a35303329b3848dc3db93","tid":224423,"uid":42536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d 奶假既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/f4/95/f49529657d8201eacf69ae6b871af278/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool-gif.com%2Fmedia%2Fgif%2Ff4%2F95%2Ff49529657d8201eacf69ae6b871af278%2Fcool.gif&h=7db7fb8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66156e6230a80c5d227373f0590480c3265bfb7d","tid":224423,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"蛇精女+滾動岩"},{"pid":"953d61ff2fc16af443796c8a843cd01ab9ce51bb","tid":224423,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d 奶假既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/f4/95/f49529657d8201eacf69ae6b871af278/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool-gi